{"tid":1628745,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［冷靜啲！］連登就嚟爆炸，五毛入侵應對方法","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:29:54.000Z","uid":285694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f49031930c9687b345772fe3106ec3a3ae59d3d3","tid":1628745,"uid":285694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:29:54.000Z","msg":"成日話叫人<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好裝修鋪頭</span></span>就係鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未必<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>人人有唔同唸法</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個諗法事實上的確比較多和理非唔認同<br />\n但呢個世界冇一個<span style=\"color: red;\">完全啱嘅行為</span><br />\n你只係需要揀一個<span style=\"color: blue;\">好處大啲嘅行為</span><br />\n我建議就真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔駛急住</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾多啲時間尋找共識<span style=\"color: red;\">討論</span>之後點做<br />\n其實<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">還掂</span></span>而家大多數黑紅鋪頭都俾人懲罰左<br />\n如果間間都打反而喺國際面前顯得好似好暴戾<br />\n其實你都係想做<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳效果</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心你打爆鋪頭傷得佢幾多<br />\n除非你拎晒佢啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有腦都知</span></span>咁樣同打劫冇分別<br />\n勇武可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔駛急住</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做返一開始勇武做嘅嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">保護和平示威者</span></span><br />\n帶定裝/着定裝先<br />\n警察一做仆街嘢e.g捉和平示威者<br />\n即刻上裝set陣勢<br />\n真係唔駛急住今日就做晒所有嘢<br />\n建議等佢裝修返好<br />\n先再裝修多一次都唔遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但打爆嘅同時要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">貼滿晒文宣做宣傳</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長期同<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">極惡政權</span></span>對打唔可以太急<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自亂陣腳</span></span><br />\n利申：發夢時前時中前，視乎鼻敏感狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗嘢要由<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">敵人角度出發</span></strong></span><br />\n比着我係五毛就做<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">分化撚</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持</span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔支持</span>嘅message都9打<br />\n等你哋分歧好似好撚大咁等你哋自行割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">支持</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔支持</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}